msgid ""
"This is an alias for C99 signbit: works for single, double and extended "
"precision, and return a non 0 value if x has the signbit set (that is the "
"number is negative)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../reference/c-api/coremath.rst:81
msgid ""
"This is an alias for  C99 copysign: return x with the same sign as y. Works "
"for any value, including inf and nan. Single and extended precisions are "
"available with suffix f and l."
msgstr ""

